Targets an area for solar bombardment, carpeting it with 40 bolts over the course of 10 seconds. Each bolt deals 25 damage to enemy units and heals non-Undead allies for 150% of that amount. Undead enemies take 10% additional damage.

Targets an area for solar bombardment, carpeting it with 40 bolts over the course of 10 seconds. Each bolt deals 50 damage to enemy units and heals non-Undead allies for 150% of that amount. Undead enemies take 10% additional damage.
